gomodel:SYNGO_1766  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"j, Immunogold labelling (arrows) localizes ErbB4 to inhibitory\nboutons (ib) contacting the AIS of pyramidal neurons, and postsynaptic to\nexcitatory boutons (eb) contacting the dendrites of interneurons (id) in\nhippocampus.\"\n\n1/11/2017 Pim\n- Localization to plasma membrane is clear from the EM pictures\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: The generation of mice used in this study has been previously described.\n\nNote: no information on species origin of constructs" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3670-7863" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0912-1514" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1766" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

